summary: Did you like the episode? Do you think it lives up to its hype? I’ve heard people say it’s one of the best episodes ever.
question: Did you like the episode? Do you think it lives up to its hype? I’ve heard people say it’s one of the best episodes ever.
answer:
I thought it was good. I think writing wise, 3x02 and 3x04 were a little more cohesive though.

I hope Bowie’s mom makes more appearances because if that’s all we get from her….yikes. I find it hard to believe a woman that clearly spoiled Bowie growing up, wouldn’t be upset about missing the opportunity to spoil her granddaughter for 14 years…..
